WEBVTT

00:00:00.546 --> 00:00:02.793
Bila sam u Njujorku
za vreme uragana Sendi

00:00:02.793 --> 00:00:05.033
i mali beli pas po imenu Maui

00:00:05.033 --> 00:00:06.918
je bio sa mnom.

00:00:06.918 --> 00:00:09.390
Pola grada je bilo u mraku
zbog nestanka struje,

00:00:09.390 --> 00:00:11.614
a ja sam živela na tamnoj strani.

00:00:11.614 --> 00:00:13.723
Mauija je mrak preplašio,

00:00:13.723 --> 00:00:15.827
pa sam morala da ga nosim
uz stepenice,

00:00:15.827 --> 00:00:18.915
zapravo najpre niz stepenice
u njegovu šetnju,

00:00:18.915 --> 00:00:20.803
i onda da ga vratim gore.

00:00:20.803 --> 00:00:23.784
Takođe sam vukla
na litre flaširane vode

00:00:23.784 --> 00:00:25.883
gore na sedmi sprat svaki dan.

00:00:25.883 --> 00:00:27.456
I tokom svega toga

00:00:27.456 --> 00:00:29.760
morala sam da držim baklju u zubima.

00:00:29.760 --> 00:00:32.404
Obližnje prodavnice ostale su
bez baterijskih lampi,